      "layout": "The site uses a full-bleed layout for its main content carousels and image galleries, allowing visuals to dominate the viewport. The page content itself is largely max-width constrained in some sections, with a centered composition for text blocks. The hero section often presents a large visual or a collection of content cards. Section rhythm is driven by substantial vertical gaps, creating clear visual breaks without explicit dividers. Content arrangement frequently uses large, impactful images or image grids where elements are often isolated. Navigation is minimal, likely restricted to a top bar menu.",
